# Sample agenda for vim-agenda-line.
# Copy to ~/.vim_calendar (or wherever g:agendaline_file points).
# Format:  HH:MM[-HH:MM]  Title [(N ppl)]
#   - end time optional -> defaults to g:agendaline_default_len minutes
#   - "(N ppl)" optional
09:30-09:45  Standup (8 ppl)
11:00-12:00  Design review with platform team (12 ppl)
14:15-14:45  1:1 with manager (2 ppl)
17:00-17:30  Deploy window
